---
title: Services | Lactation Consultant
description: Choose antenatal or postnatal lactation support based on where you are in your feeding journey.
layout: layouts/base.njk
---

<main class="bg-natural-light flex-grow px-4 py-8 text-warm-gray">
  <section class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl flex flex-col items-center">
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-center text-5xl">Services</h1>

        <div class="flex gap-8 flex-col lg:flex-row mt-4">
            <a href="/antenatal/" class="group mt-5 block w-full max-w-[360px] overflow-hidden rounded-5xl border-2 border-warm-gray-light bg-white p-0 shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-warm-gray focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-warm-gray-light focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-natural-100">
                <div class="h-[260px] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-none border-0 lg:h-[320px]">
                    {% image "./src/assets/images/antenatal-services.jpg", "Woman with pregnant stomach", "320px", "object-cover object-center w-full h-full" %}
                </div>
                <div class="px-4 pb-4">
                    <h2 class="mt-4 text-center text-2xl font-semibold transition-colors group-hover:text-warm-gray-light">Antenatal</h2>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-center px-4">Prepare for breastfeeding before birth with practical, confidence-building guidance.</p>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/postnatal/" class="group mt-5 block w-full max-w-[360px] overflow-hidden rounded-5xl border-2 border-warm-gray-light bg-white p-0 shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-warm-gray focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-warm-gray-light focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-natural-100">
                <div class="h-[260px] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-none border-0 lg:h-[320px]">
                    {% image "./src/assets/images/postnatal-services.jpg", "Mother breastfeeding baby", "320px", "object-cover object-center w-full h-full" %}
                </div>
                <div class="px-4 pb-4">
                    <h2 class="mt-4 text-center text-2xl font-semibold transition-colors group-hover:text-warm-gray-light">Postnatal</h2>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-center px-4">Get support after birth for latch, comfort, milk supply, and feeding progress.</p>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <p class="font-bold mt-10 text-center">No referral is necessary for appointments, and consults are not dependant on place of delivery. 
            Any mum, from any location can access our support.</p>
  </section>
</main>
